OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FA cleanup operation is underway in
OL,8,FSouthampton after protesters clashed
OL,9,Fwith police on Tuesday night, as ITV
OL,10,FNews' Jonathan Swain reports
OL,12,FPolice carrying riot shields clashed
OL,13,Fwith protesters who gathered in
OL,14,FSouthampton over the police handling
OL,15,Fof the murder of Henry Nowak, despite
OL,16,Fcalls for calm.
OL,18,FTwo people were arrested after the
OL,19,Funrest, according to policing minister
OL,20,FSarah Jones, who urged people not to
OL,21,F"overreact".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FSpeaking to Time Radio on Wednesday,
OL,8,FMs Jones called some of the scenes
OL,9,Ffrom the protest "unacceptable" and
OL,10,Fsaid the arrests were for assault of a
OL,11,Fpolice officer, and possession of a
OL,12,Fweapon.
OL,14,FHundreds gathered outside Southampton
OL,15,FCentral Police Station shortly before
OL,16,F6pm on Tuesday, where Tommy Robinson
OL,17,Fand Laurence Fox were among those who
OL,18,Fspoke to the crowd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,8,Fgroup walked across town to the area
OL,9,Fof Portswood.
OL,11,FA police helicopter hovered overhead
OL,12,Fas police officers were pelted with
OL,13,Fstones and bricks while demonstrators
OL,14,Fchanted "Henry, Henry".
OL,16,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,17,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,18,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,19,Fback from the line they had been
OL,20,Fholding.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
