OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,8,Freported live at the scene
OL,10,FTensions have been rising since police
OL,11,Fbodycam footage was released on Monday
OL,12,Fnight, showing an officer handcuffing
OL,13,FMr Nowak as he lay dying from stab
OL,14,Fwounds.
OL,16,FThe footage was made public after
OL,17,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,18,Ffor murdering the 18-year-old
OL,19,FUniversity of Southampton student with
OL,20,Fa Sikh ceremonial knife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,8,Fverdict on Monday, Mr Nowak's father
OL,9,FMark, had said that his family wanted
OL,10,Fto use Henry's story "to make change
OL,11,Ffor the better" rather than as fuel
OL,12,Ffor conflict.
OL,14,F"We do not want his death to be used
OL,15,Fto create further division, hatred or
OL,16,Ftension. We want his story to help
OL,17,Fmake our streets safer for everyone,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
