PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThat plea was reiterated by the Home
OL,8,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood on Tuesday
OL,9,Fafter Reform UK leader Nigel Farage
OL,10,Fissued a statement about the case.
OL,12,FShe reacted to Tuesday night's protest
OL,13,Fwith a post on X, calling the scenes
OL,14,F"completely unacceptable" and saying:
OL,15,F"There can be no justification for
OL,16,Fhijacking this tragedy to stir up
OL,17,Fviolence and disorder."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"I thank the police who have tonight
OL,8,Fshown great bravery and calm in the
OL,9,Fface of disgraceful violence directed
OL,10,Fat them," she added.
OL,12,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,13,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,14,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,15,Fknife with a 21cm blade prosecutors
OL,16,Fsaid was a kirpan, which he carried as
OL,17,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
