FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FHe had previously been investigated by
OL,8,Fpolice in 2023 on suspicion of
OL,9,Fstealing ceremonial blades from a Sikh
OL,10,Ftemple in Southampton but no further
OL,11,Faction was taken.
OL,13,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,F(NPCC) announced it would review anti-
OL,15,Fracism guidance ` called the Race
OL,16,FAction Plan ` that some have blamed
OL,17,Ffor the actions of the officers who
OL,18,Farrested Mr Nowak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FNPCC chairman Gavin Stephens said: "We
OL,8,Fare listening to legitimate concerns
OL,9,Fabout how some of these commitments
OL,10,Fare worded or phrased, and where
OL,11,Fneeded we can and will make changes,
OL,12,Fbut this should not detract from the
OL,13,Fintent, which is to improve the
OL,14,Fquality of policing."
OL,16,FEarlier on Tuesday Hampshire Police
OL,17,Fsaid an officer not connected to the
OL,18,Fcase had faced death threats after
OL,19,Fbeing misidentified in online posts.
OL,26,@oD@dOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
