CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780589464
OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FIn a post on X, the force said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the desire for answers about
OL,9,Fthe police response that night" and
OL,10,Fwarned people not to indulge in
OL,11,F"harmful online speculation".
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,14,Fsaid he "felt sick" watching
OL,15,F"harrowing" footage of police
OL,16,Fhandcuffing Mr Nowak and said there
OL,17,Fare "serious questions" to answer
OL,18,Fabout the case.
OL,26,@oD@aOUqD@_O]sD@AOUsD@\O]vD@IOUvD@SO]wD@
OL,26,AAOUwD@KO]yD@EOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
