OL,3,CProtesters accused of 'hijacking'
OL,4,CHenry Nowak tragedy after clash with
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThere needs to be an examination into
OL,8,Fhow "accusations of racism" informed
OL,9,Fthe police's decision-making in the
OL,10,Fcase, he added.
OL,12,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,13,Freport on the case within the next
OL,14,Fthree months.
OL,16,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC) said its independent
OL,18,Finvestigation "remains ongoing".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
